        public CholeskyDecomposition​(Matrix A)
        Constructs CholeskyDecomposition object, received a Matrix object to decompose a matrix into Cholesky decomposition method.
        Parameters:
        A - Matrix object to Cholesky factorization.
        Throws:
        MatrixSizeException - if a A matrix is non-square.
